{"tid":1868790,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國副總統彭斯指英國讓華為參與5G是美英兩國的問題","createTime":"2020-02-07T19:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T19:26:02.000Z","uid":125193,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d78dc797b024e7117cb1ffef5e79ebbf1c8f1bd9","tid":1868790,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T19:24:26.000Z","msg":"美國副總統彭斯表示，英國決定讓中國電訊設備商華為，有限度參與5G網絡建設，仍然是美英兩國之間的問題。被問到會否影響兩國達成貿易協議，彭斯說拭目以待。<br />\n<br />\n不過，白宮經濟顧問庫德洛說，英國的決定不會妨礙兩國尋求達成貿易協議，又指美國會與英國在5G方面合作，美國希望達成自貿協議。<br />\n<br />\n被問到總統特朗普據報與英國首相約翰遜通電話時爭吵，會否影響兩國達成協議，庫德洛表明不會，又質疑報道的真實性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507358-20200208.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507358-20200208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxnyEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=9e2e7036\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507358-20200208.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=44713a7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507358-20200208.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"aee9339474ceda76432dfc59fe7e1cc5ad639512","tid":1868790,"uid":281328,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T19:26:02.000Z","msg":"英國開門，美國殺敵？"}]}